      <ab type="lido:objectDescriptionSet">The still photograph shows a barefoot man dressed in traditional costume alongside a donkey carrying wooden sticks.</ab>
      <ab subtype="comment" type="lido:objectDescriptionSet">The feature ‘Buntăt na robite’ (’Riot of the Slaves’) was the first sound film to be produced in Bulgaria. It was produced in collaboration with an Austrian film production company. Vasil Gendov was the producer and director.</ab>
